{"tid":1953413,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"慶祝愚人節！IU拍片扮揸車：終於考到車牌","createTime":"2020-04-01T07:28:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T08:24:51.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8f1550290c4e5da14035838a980d13973762e099","tid":1953413,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T07:28:44.000Z","msg":"今日是愚人節，韓國26歲靚聲女歌手IU昨晚在個人YouTube頻道「IU TV」公開試車片，並指自己終於考到車牌：「我買咗車啦，終於喺30歲前考到車牌，我要透過『IU TV』公開呢個歷史時刻。」不少粉絲都好奇地問：「IU係幾時考咗車牌㗎？」<br />\n<br />\n其實IU是趁愚人節跟大家開玩笑，IU之後公開假軚盤，而影片的畫面其實是經過左右調轉編輯，真正的司機是坐在身旁的父親，IU其實對駕駛毫無認識，更問父親如何開轉向燈，而IU為了不穿崩，更將面上的墨畫到相反方向，做戲做足全套！<br />\n<br />\n除了有粉絲被IU騙到，連女星宋慧喬都被呃到，更在IU的Instagram影片留下合十祈禱和玫瑰花的表情符號，似乎是祝IU試車成功，而朴率美亦以為IU考到車牌，被粉絲提醒後才留言說：「原來被騙啦！」"},{"pid":"d2c6c06eb4b2684ba33089f06b5e778768cc5728","tid":1953413,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T07:29:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200401/photo/bkn-20200401122240126-0401_00862_001_01b.jpg?20200401133714\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200401%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200401122240126-0401_00862_001_01b.jpg%3F20200401133714&h=aa1d4a88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200401/photo/bkn-20200401122240126-0401_00862_001_02b.jpg?20200401133714\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200401%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200401122240126-0401_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20200401133714&h=f203e3a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200401/photo/bkn-20200401122240126-0401_00862_001_03b.jpg?20200401133714\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200401%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200401122240126-0401_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20200401133714&h=73268687&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertain